Name: Base Station License, Approval, Teito America, Inc., Queens
Title: A Local Law in relation to the approval of a determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Teito America, Inc. also known as Tieton America Inc. also known as Tieto America Inc. for a license to operate a new base station in the borough of Queens.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

      Section one.  The determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Teito America, Inc. also known as Tieton America Inc. also known as Tieto America Inc. for a license to operate a new base station at 133-43 Roosevelt Avenue in the borough of Queens is hereby approved. 
      ï¿½2. This local law shall take effect immediately.
